**New files:**

* `README.md`: This file will contain a description of the project, as well as instructions on how to use the proxy.
* `package.json`: This file will contain the project's dependencies and other metadata.
* `index.js`: This file will contain the main code for the proxy.
* `.env`: This file will contain the proxy's configuration settings.

**File structure:**

```
├── LICENSE
├── README.md
├── package.json
├── index.js
└── .env
```